    <item>
      <title>就业数据引发波动，比特币跌至一个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/bitcoin-btc-taking-cue-from-stocks-as-us-jobs-data-loom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国就业报告令人失望，数字资产在市场动荡的交易时段中受到影响，比特币和其他加密货币大幅下跌，抹去了早前的涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/bitcoin-btc-taking-cue-from-stocks-as-us-jobs-data-loom</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 05:03:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
